            <title>[OWB-697] Non-Static Loggers leads to NonSerizializableException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OWB-697</link>
                <project id="12310844" key="OWB">OpenWebBeans</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;List of loggers which can be made static:&lt;br/&gt;
PluginLoader&lt;br/&gt;
AbstractMetaDataDiscovery&lt;br/&gt;
OsgiMetaDataScannerService&lt;br/&gt;
FailOverBag&lt;br/&gt;
FailOverBagWrapper&lt;/p&gt;

