                            <comment id="13447273" author="tandraschko" created="Mon, 3 Sep 2012 13:38:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I attached a patch to make the first loggers static. Could anyone check if we should change WebContainerLifecycle and AbstractLifeCycle?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
